WEBVTT

01:27.370 --> 01:31.900
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.130 --> 01:34.940
[Episode 4]

01:47.620 --> 01:50.160
[Lihai Toll Station]

01:52.840 --> 01:53.400
Mom,

01:53.680 --> 01:55.430
do hamsters get carsick?

01:58.640 --> 02:00.000
Do we have to bring it?

02:00.710 --> 02:01.560
How about

02:02.000 --> 02:04.600
we ask Aunt Feng
to take care of it for a few days?

02:04.760 --> 02:05.590
You forgot—

02:05.870 --> 02:07.800
Aunt Feng is terrified of rodents.

02:08.520 --> 02:10.190
I'll talk to Grandma.

02:10.190 --> 02:11.120
It's very clean.

02:11.150 --> 02:12.350
It's not dirty at all.

02:31.400 --> 02:32.590
Hello, Dr. Luo.

02:34.510 --> 02:35.670
I'm sorry, Ms. Yan.

02:36.280 --> 02:37.810
You sent me so many messages,

02:37.810 --> 02:39.070
and I just saw them now.

02:40.079 --> 02:41.360
I only sent two.

02:41.790 --> 02:43.310
I've been on a business trip
these past few days

02:43.310 --> 02:45.380
and didn't have time to check my phone.

02:45.380 --> 02:47.220
Do you need any help?

02:49.650 --> 02:50.630
The thing is...

02:56.520 --> 02:59.450
I want to take Jiale back
to my hometown for a few days.

03:00.690 --> 03:02.020
I took your advice

03:02.520 --> 03:03.460
and want him

03:03.800 --> 03:06.060
to say a proper goodbye to his Godmother.

03:06.590 --> 03:08.700
And this hamster...

03:10.610 --> 03:12.610
It's inconvenient to bring, right?

03:13.330 --> 03:14.450
I'm really sorry.

03:14.770 --> 03:17.370
I originally wanted
to help ease Jiale's mood.

03:17.400 --> 03:19.930
I didn't expect it
to become a trouble for you.

03:19.960 --> 03:20.820
How about this?

03:21.320 --> 03:22.840
You leave more food for it.

03:22.940 --> 03:24.620
It'll be fine for two or three days.

03:24.620 --> 03:26.870
My work in Gangdao isn't finished yet,

03:27.480 --> 03:28.940
so I can't rush back today.

03:29.590 --> 03:30.600
Forget it.

03:31.079 --> 03:32.280
We'll bring it along.

03:32.910 --> 03:34.930
Leaving the hamster alone at home—

03:35.230 --> 03:36.550
we won't be at ease

03:36.750 --> 03:38.480
if it runs out of food and water.

03:38.570 --> 03:40.110
I really made it hard for you.

03:40.110 --> 03:41.170
When you come back,

03:41.910 --> 03:43.240
you must give me a chance

03:43.310 --> 03:44.870
to treat you to a nice meal.

03:45.280 --> 03:46.079
No need.

03:46.470 --> 03:47.000
You must.

03:47.510 --> 03:48.170
Promise me.

03:48.720 --> 03:50.720
I also want to thank Jiale in person.

03:51.030 --> 03:51.470
Okay.

03:52.360 --> 03:52.990
Great.

03:53.520 --> 03:54.280
It's a deal.

03:54.840 --> 03:56.150
Drive carefully.

03:56.400 --> 03:58.060
Call me as soon as you get back.

03:58.160 --> 03:58.900
You promise.

04:00.260 --> 04:01.340
I gotta go.

04:01.840 --> 04:03.100
I still have patients.

04:04.280 --> 04:05.400
See you when you get back.

04:05.400 --> 04:06.750
Okay. Bye.

04:15.520 --> 04:16.980
Keep your eyes on the road.

04:30.830 --> 04:32.270
I was wrong. I was wrong.

04:32.270 --> 04:33.190
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

04:33.190 --> 04:35.390
I beg you. I beg you.

04:35.510 --> 04:37.620
Please.

04:38.480 --> 04:39.880
Raise your head a little.

04:47.850 --> 04:49.409
So, what exactly happened?

04:52.830 --> 04:53.830
He was drunk.

04:54.870 --> 04:56.040
After he got home,

04:56.600 --> 04:57.530
he went straight

04:57.600 --> 04:58.930
to bed.

05:00.190 --> 05:01.870
I got him a glass of water.

05:02.600 --> 05:03.240
And then?

05:04.120 --> 05:05.430
And then... And then...

05:05.430 --> 05:06.310
I... I...

05:07.600 --> 05:09.350
I hit her.

05:09.920 --> 05:12.160
Then he suddenly got up,

05:14.390 --> 05:15.680
grabbed me by the neck,

05:15.680 --> 05:17.310
and started beating me.

05:19.390 --> 05:20.310
Why are you beating me?

05:20.310 --> 05:21.330
Why?

05:23.070 --> 05:24.510
Do I need a reason?

05:24.600 --> 05:26.790
I can beat you if I'm unhappy!

05:29.830 --> 05:30.360
Run?

05:33.920 --> 05:34.520
No.

05:34.870 --> 05:36.750
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

05:36.800 --> 05:38.200
You think that's enough?

05:39.720 --> 05:41.070
I put a roof over your head,

05:41.070 --> 05:42.390
and you despise me?

05:42.680 --> 05:44.120
I don't know why.

05:44.120 --> 05:45.870
I really don't know why.

05:49.390 --> 05:51.870
I... I really can't remember.

05:52.920 --> 05:54.680
After I went back,

05:54.680 --> 05:55.610
she seemed to...

05:56.720 --> 05:58.040
she seemed to keep asking me.

05:58.040 --> 05:58.920
She asked me

05:59.159 --> 06:01.490
if I had another woman on the side.

06:01.560 --> 06:02.720
So you hit her?

06:30.190 --> 06:31.560
So I...

06:31.920 --> 06:33.920
I'm a bastard.

06:34.270 --> 06:35.430
I'm a bastard.

06:35.430 --> 06:37.659
I... I'm sorry to her.

06:37.830 --> 06:39.159
-She's such a good woman.
-I failed her.

06:39.159 --> 06:40.560
But you beat her like this.

06:40.560 --> 06:41.950
Hearing you might be detained,

06:41.950 --> 06:43.350
she even pleaded for you.

06:44.390 --> 06:45.920
She really wants to settle?

06:46.040 --> 06:47.090
After all this,

06:47.480 --> 06:50.010
are you sure you still want
to settle with him?

07:04.240 --> 07:05.600
Will Godfather come?

07:06.240 --> 07:07.240
Probably not.

07:08.320 --> 07:09.520
He seems pretty busy.

07:10.680 --> 07:13.240
Is Godfather too sad?

07:13.980 --> 07:15.640
After Godmother passed away,

07:15.950 --> 07:17.950
he doesn't even play games anymore.

07:18.280 --> 07:19.810
If Godmother can't see him,

07:20.270 --> 07:21.680
will she be sad?

07:32.600 --> 07:33.130
Let's go.

07:33.680 --> 07:34.210
Let's go.

07:36.070 --> 07:36.870
Grandma Jian.

07:37.610 --> 07:39.520
Why did you move here?

07:39.750 --> 07:41.080
It's too run-down here.

07:41.480 --> 07:42.040
Jiale,

07:42.460 --> 07:43.850
don't talk nonsense.

07:44.070 --> 07:45.520
We sold the old house.

07:46.070 --> 07:48.980
Now it's just me and Grandma Jian.

07:49.700 --> 07:51.159
This room is enough for us.

07:53.310 --> 07:54.070
Uncle,

07:54.750 --> 07:57.240
I want to talk to you
about Leilei's house.

08:00.480 --> 08:01.550
Before,

08:02.480 --> 08:04.300
she mortgaged the house.

08:04.630 --> 08:06.560
Now they are coming to take it away.

08:08.600 --> 08:09.870
I should have known it.

08:11.360 --> 08:12.460
This child...

08:12.870 --> 08:14.040
I know her too well.

08:15.600 --> 08:16.800
If she weren't driven to a corner

08:16.800 --> 08:18.210
and had no other choice,

08:19.240 --> 08:21.970
she wouldn't have touched
other people's money.

08:33.159 --> 08:33.650
[Officer Li]

08:33.679 --> 08:34.210
[Is he Xia Yi?]

08:38.220 --> 08:38.620
Yes.

08:38.809 --> 08:40.250
It's Xu's photo.

08:41.030 --> 08:41.600
Before this,

08:41.600 --> 08:43.750
didn't you police officers
come to investigate?

08:43.750 --> 08:44.550
The person you are looking for

08:44.550 --> 08:45.360
is not him.

08:45.510 --> 08:47.270
Other police officers have looked for him?

08:47.270 --> 08:47.850
Yes.

08:47.910 --> 08:49.040
Not only the police,

08:49.080 --> 08:51.380
but also two or three groups
of young girls.

08:49.710 --> 08:50.420
[Is he Xia Yi?]

08:50.440 --> 08:54.520
[He isn't Xia Yi.]

08:51.480 --> 08:53.790
They said Xu was in online relationships
with them,

08:53.790 --> 08:54.750
asked them to invest,

08:54.750 --> 08:56.790
and swindled them out of a lot of money.

08:56.790 --> 08:57.630
Mr. Xing,

08:58.200 --> 08:59.780
do you have a group photo

08:59.800 --> 09:01.600
of all your rescue team members?

09:01.710 --> 09:02.390
Yes.

09:06.270 --> 09:06.790
Xu

09:06.790 --> 09:08.370
is a good guy in our team.

09:09.150 --> 09:10.810
A while ago, during a mission,

09:11.080 --> 09:12.360
he was injured while saving someone.

09:12.360 --> 09:13.390
He's been in the hospital,

09:13.390 --> 09:14.450
in a coma.

09:14.870 --> 09:15.870
It was just last week

09:15.870 --> 09:17.530
that his hand could move a bit.

09:17.720 --> 09:19.150
When they checked the timeline,
it didn't match at all—

09:19.150 --> 09:20.550
They found it was not him.

09:21.960 --> 09:22.750
Everyone is here.

09:22.750 --> 09:23.150
Okay.

09:25.200 --> 09:26.950
Which bastard

09:27.240 --> 09:29.130
used Xu's photo to scam people?

09:29.200 --> 09:30.600
That's just disgusting.

09:32.870 --> 09:34.670
Is there one person named Xia Yi?

09:34.960 --> 09:37.200
There's no one
with the last name Xia on our team.

09:37.200 --> 09:39.150
A woman also called to ask about him.

09:39.150 --> 09:40.360
When we're busy,

09:40.440 --> 09:42.600
we have some temporary volunteers
to help out.

09:42.600 --> 09:43.840
But there were too many people,

09:43.840 --> 09:45.170
so I couldn't remember.

09:47.870 --> 09:48.270
Okay.

09:48.970 --> 09:49.590
Thank you.

09:50.360 --> 09:50.600
Thank you.

09:50.480 --> 09:53.100
[Officer Li]

09:50.630 --> 09:51.230
Take care.

09:51.870 --> 09:52.480
Then,

09:52.480 --> 09:53.980
let's leave a contact method.

09:53.100 --> 09:55.320
[Xia Yi is not in this photo.]

09:54.360 --> 09:56.000
If there are any important clues,

09:56.000 --> 09:57.400
contact me immediately.

09:57.440 --> 09:57.840
Okay.

09:57.870 --> 09:58.240
Okay.

09:58.240 --> 09:58.570
Okay.

09:58.820 --> 09:59.080
Here.

09:59.080 --> 09:59.410
Here.

10:00.930 --> 10:02.010
This is my number. Take it down.

10:01.010 --> 10:01.940
[Xia Yi is not in this photo.]

10:01.960 --> 10:04.980
[Thank you for your investigation.
Thank you.]

10:02.030 --> 10:02.360
Okay.

10:02.820 --> 10:03.670
I will just take it down.

10:03.670 --> 10:04.000
Here.

10:05.010 --> 10:06.890
[I'm sorry.
I shouldn't have said that to you.]

10:32.870 --> 10:33.530
Godmother.

10:33.770 --> 10:34.910
I miss you so much.

10:35.910 --> 10:38.710
Whenever I think
of not being able to see you again,

10:39.430 --> 10:40.800
I get so scared.

10:42.070 --> 10:43.500
I really want to see you,

10:45.100 --> 10:46.980
but I can't even dream about you.

10:49.880 --> 10:51.010
I dreamed about her.

10:52.120 --> 10:52.720
Xia.

10:53.360 --> 10:54.120
You are here.

10:54.240 --> 10:54.960
Xia is here.

10:54.960 --> 10:55.550
Uncle. Auntie.

10:55.550 --> 10:56.210
Godfather.

10:58.390 --> 10:59.450
It has been 35 days.

11:00.150 --> 11:01.270
I believe Leilei

11:01.960 --> 11:03.420
will come back to visit us.

11:18.670 --> 11:19.360
Leilei.

11:20.480 --> 11:21.480
It was my fault

11:21.960 --> 11:23.690
for not taking good care of you.

11:24.080 --> 11:25.000
We agreed

11:25.750 --> 11:27.440
to use your favorite

11:27.440 --> 11:29.570
tulips for the bouquet at our wedding.

11:30.360 --> 11:32.620
But too bad I don't have
that kind of luck.

11:44.600 --> 11:45.120
Jiale,

11:46.000 --> 11:47.200
you've grown taller.

11:49.600 --> 11:50.240
Later,

11:51.030 --> 11:53.360
I need to pay the cemetery management fee.

11:53.470 --> 11:54.470
You come with me.

11:58.630 --> 11:59.760
Who are you, really?

12:00.720 --> 12:02.120
What did you do to Leilei?

12:05.490 --> 12:06.420
I've told Leilei

12:06.870 --> 12:08.360
about this before.

12:10.040 --> 12:11.770
Actually, my name is not Xia Yi.

12:12.820 --> 12:14.630
I'm an overseas Pazion Chinese.

12:15.060 --> 12:17.060
My family is in the gem business.

12:18.520 --> 12:21.630
Over the past couple of years, they've been
gradually handing the business over to me

12:21.630 --> 12:23.960
and sent me here
to explore the Chinese market.

12:23.960 --> 12:25.690
To make doing business easier,

12:26.140 --> 12:28.060
I gave myself a Chinese name—

12:28.720 --> 12:29.270
Xia Yi.

12:29.940 --> 12:31.640
Then, when something happened to Leilei,

12:31.640 --> 12:33.620
why didn't you go to the police?

12:34.960 --> 12:35.630
You know,

12:35.980 --> 12:37.790
a gemstone can be worth ten thousand,

12:37.790 --> 12:39.390
a hundred thousand, or even more.

12:39.390 --> 12:40.440
There's even jade gambling.

12:40.440 --> 12:43.170
There's a lot of room
to operate in this business.

12:44.030 --> 12:46.000
With our family business running
for so many years,

12:46.000 --> 12:48.060
there are bound to be some gray areas.

12:49.390 --> 12:50.750
So over the past years,

12:51.630 --> 12:52.600
I've tried my best to avoid

12:52.600 --> 12:54.000
dealing with the police.

12:54.750 --> 12:56.200
So you lied to the police

12:56.390 --> 12:58.120
and told them you were doing rescue work?

12:58.120 --> 12:59.580
It was all fake, wasn't it?

12:59.890 --> 13:01.150
Not entirely.

13:02.440 --> 13:04.390
I know my business isn't honorable,

13:04.390 --> 13:06.520
so I always wanted to do some good deeds

13:06.840 --> 13:08.720
to atone for my sins.

13:09.390 --> 13:11.240
But to join a formal rescue team,

13:11.630 --> 13:13.840
I have to register
with the Civil Affairs Bureau.

13:13.840 --> 13:14.640
I had no choice

13:15.440 --> 13:17.100
but to just help out

13:17.200 --> 13:18.210
and volunteer.

13:19.000 --> 13:20.600
Leilei knew about this, too.

13:21.630 --> 13:22.840
Then did Leilei know

13:23.910 --> 13:25.360
that the watches

13:25.510 --> 13:25.870
and bags you gave her

13:25.870 --> 13:26.870
were all fake?

13:27.440 --> 13:28.750
I had the things you gave her

13:28.750 --> 13:30.010
appraised.

13:30.240 --> 13:31.440
Not a single one is real.

13:31.440 --> 13:32.600
Not even one.

13:33.000 --> 13:34.720
How could they be fake?

13:35.040 --> 13:37.240
I picked them out
with Leilei at the boutiques.

13:37.240 --> 13:39.040
We have receipts for all of them.

13:40.550 --> 13:42.200
I'll show you the transaction records,

13:42.200 --> 13:42.720
okay?

13:46.290 --> 13:47.070
Never mind.

13:47.480 --> 13:48.410
Look at this one.

13:50.360 --> 13:51.450
How does it look?

13:52.440 --> 13:54.200
Do you really think it looks good?

13:54.200 --> 13:55.110
Yes, it does.

13:55.150 --> 13:56.440
But isn't it a bit expensive?

13:56.440 --> 13:57.150
And

13:57.320 --> 13:59.360
aren't the diamonds a bit too much?

13:59.390 --> 14:00.720
It has to be over the top.

14:00.790 --> 14:03.080
My girl deserves
something sparkly like this

14:03.080 --> 14:05.430
to outshine those rich clients of yours.

14:06.030 --> 14:06.870
Stop it.

14:07.550 --> 14:08.410
Check, please.

14:10.270 --> 14:11.090
Leilei

14:12.260 --> 14:13.920
must have been short on money,

14:14.510 --> 14:16.260
so she sold the real ones,

14:16.550 --> 14:17.950
swapped them with fakes,

14:19.300 --> 14:21.160
and made sure I wouldn't find out.

14:23.320 --> 14:24.840
Why would she do that?

14:27.510 --> 14:28.570
There's something

14:29.380 --> 14:30.980
I've never told anyone.

14:32.030 --> 14:33.320
I once accidentally

14:34.240 --> 14:35.630
found that kind of photo

14:37.050 --> 14:38.550
in Leilei's phone.

14:39.900 --> 14:40.960
What kind of photo?

14:42.890 --> 14:44.410
Nude photos taken

14:45.200 --> 14:46.330
while holding her ID.

14:45.320 --> 14:47.280
[Name: Jian Leilei]

14:51.130 --> 14:51.930
Are you saying

14:52.440 --> 14:53.240
that Leilei

14:54.200 --> 14:56.800
got involved in one of
those nude loan schemes?

14:58.150 --> 14:59.420
So I guess

14:59.960 --> 15:01.660
Leilei's tattoo

15:02.550 --> 15:04.120
was also done

15:04.120 --> 15:05.120
at their request.

15:07.910 --> 15:09.040
That's impossible.

15:20.030 --> 15:20.580
This

15:21.640 --> 15:24.010
is the avatar you used in the game.

15:24.510 --> 15:26.200
Leilei had an octopus tattoo.

15:27.630 --> 15:29.960
If her tattoo had nothing to do with you,

15:30.790 --> 15:31.840
why did you

15:32.200 --> 15:34.080
use an octopus as your avatar?

15:34.950 --> 15:35.530
Why?

15:36.600 --> 15:38.000
Because I love Leilei.

15:38.910 --> 15:39.630
Since I love her,

15:39.630 --> 15:40.750
I must love everything about her,

15:40.750 --> 15:42.750
including her flaws.

15:43.440 --> 15:45.360
I changed my avatar to this

15:45.380 --> 15:47.080
just to let her know

15:48.120 --> 15:49.720
that I don't mind her past.

15:56.910 --> 15:57.970
That can't be real.

15:58.640 --> 16:00.100
If that's really the case,

16:02.010 --> 16:04.040
how could I not feel anything?

16:05.330 --> 16:06.960
How could I not know anything?

16:06.960 --> 16:09.360
That's because
she didn't want you to know.

16:10.180 --> 16:11.540
In her heart,

16:11.910 --> 16:14.030
you and Jiale were much more
important than me.

16:14.030 --> 16:14.960
In her suicide note,

16:14.960 --> 16:16.560
she didn't mention me at all.

16:17.730 --> 16:19.180
She only mentioned you,

16:20.440 --> 16:21.270
didn't she?

16:34.420 --> 16:35.780
You can go verify it.

16:34.560 --> 16:37.930
[Name: Pongsri Leekpa]

16:36.150 --> 16:38.030
The worst that can happen
is my family's business gets exposed.

16:38.030 --> 16:39.790
I'll just be deported

16:40.390 --> 16:42.050
and never be able to come back.

16:44.640 --> 16:45.360
I will.

16:47.370 --> 16:48.310
[Name: Pongsri Leekpa]

16:49.670 --> 16:50.470
[Name: Pongsri Leekpa]

17:02.430 --> 17:05.250
Every time Godmother
peels an apple for me,

17:05.589 --> 17:06.589
she'd cut it

17:06.589 --> 17:08.319
into little bunny shapes, too.

17:09.030 --> 17:10.310
Then have some more.

17:14.240 --> 17:14.970
Coming.

17:21.440 --> 17:22.310
Are the cemetery matters

17:22.310 --> 17:23.140
taken care of?

17:23.240 --> 17:24.700
Yes. Don't worry.

17:25.240 --> 17:26.339
Come sit for a while.

17:26.339 --> 17:27.170
I won't sit.

17:27.240 --> 17:28.590
We have to go to my mom's.

17:37.540 --> 17:38.000
Jiale,

17:38.420 --> 17:39.040
let's go.

17:46.850 --> 17:47.730
Grandpa Jian,

17:48.400 --> 17:51.240
can you help me take care
of the hamster tonight?

17:51.240 --> 17:52.160
No problem.

17:52.910 --> 17:54.330
I'll take it tomorrow.

17:54.730 --> 17:56.270
Don't bother Grandpa Jian.

17:57.160 --> 17:57.960
Don't be silly.

17:57.960 --> 17:59.020
Just leave it here.

17:59.310 --> 18:00.920
Your mom is a clean freak.

18:02.510 --> 18:04.870
When Leilei was little, she had a kitten.

18:05.000 --> 18:06.550
She wanted to give you one of its babies,

18:06.550 --> 18:08.210
but you didn't dare to take it.

18:12.130 --> 18:13.360
I mean,

18:13.550 --> 18:15.830
when you come to pick up
the hamster tomorrow,

18:15.830 --> 18:17.650
I can see Jiale again,

18:17.750 --> 18:18.270
right?

18:19.160 --> 18:19.790
Good boy.

18:20.340 --> 18:21.070
Good boy.

18:23.190 --> 18:24.560
Say hi to your mom for me.

18:25.830 --> 18:26.760
We'll get going.

18:27.270 --> 18:28.110
Go on.

18:29.110 --> 18:31.110
Bye-bye, Grandpa and Grandma Jian.

18:34.440 --> 18:35.040
Take care.

19:00.720 --> 19:03.000
Why were you so mean to Godfather today?

19:04.070 --> 19:04.920
Godmother is gone.

19:04.920 --> 19:06.720
He's had it hard enough already.

19:09.610 --> 19:11.340
You really like him, don't you?

19:11.790 --> 19:12.680
Of course.

19:13.240 --> 19:14.760
He's not just nice to me.

19:15.070 --> 19:16.930
He treats Godmother even better.

19:17.000 --> 19:19.350
Every time Godmother was with him,

19:19.380 --> 19:20.740
she laughed so happily.

19:37.310 --> 19:37.880
Can you handle them?

19:37.880 --> 19:38.400
Yes.

19:38.640 --> 19:39.170
Let's go.

19:42.010 --> 19:45.840
[No Soliciting]

19:44.790 --> 19:45.480
Be good

19:45.480 --> 19:46.400
at Grandma's.

19:46.400 --> 19:47.350
Got it?

19:52.030 --> 19:52.480
Mom.

19:53.400 --> 19:53.930
Grandma.

19:54.830 --> 19:55.690
Jiale, come in.

19:55.880 --> 19:56.340
Come in.

19:58.440 --> 19:59.220
Here.

19:59.350 --> 20:00.410
Change your shoes.

20:01.720 --> 20:03.520
Don't forget to wash your hands.

20:09.720 --> 20:10.580
You go in first.

20:17.880 --> 20:18.810
Good boy, Jiale.

20:19.920 --> 20:20.790
Do it with your mom.

20:20.790 --> 20:21.390
Come here.

20:26.480 --> 20:26.890
Dad.

20:27.070 --> 20:28.390
We're here to see Mom.

20:28.750 --> 20:29.810
Jiale is back, too.

20:32.550 --> 20:33.270
Grandpa.

20:33.920 --> 20:35.310
Mom told me

20:35.640 --> 20:36.960
she missed you a lot.

20:37.270 --> 20:38.470
How dare she say that?

20:39.350 --> 20:41.200
She came back and didn't
even visit her family first,

20:41.200 --> 20:42.900
but ran off to show filial piety
at someone else's house.

20:42.900 --> 20:44.980
But today is my Godmother's death anniversary.

20:44.980 --> 20:46.240
-No buts.
-Godmother—

20:47.070 --> 20:48.800
Burn the incense before we eat.

20:59.000 --> 21:00.720
Come on, Jiale. Time for bed.

21:01.240 --> 21:01.960
Wait a minute.

21:01.960 --> 21:03.200
I need to sort out

21:03.200 --> 21:04.590
Godmother's photos on my pad

21:04.590 --> 21:06.450
and forward them to Grandpa Jian.

21:06.680 --> 21:07.480
You still have to sleep.

21:07.480 --> 21:08.590
Look what time it is.

21:08.590 --> 21:09.590
Wait a minute!

21:09.590 --> 21:10.320
Be a good boy.

21:10.750 --> 21:11.110
Wait.

21:21.110 --> 21:21.920
You

21:22.110 --> 21:23.740
don't spoil Jiale too much.

21:25.510 --> 21:27.710
Leilei's matter has a big impact on him.

21:28.640 --> 21:29.960
And he means well.

21:31.750 --> 21:33.810
I shouldn't speak ill of the dead.

21:35.000 --> 21:35.640
But,

21:35.640 --> 21:37.110
you young people

21:37.510 --> 21:39.100
are just too selfish,

21:39.880 --> 21:41.890
making the old bury the young.

21:42.030 --> 21:43.400
How could

21:43.400 --> 21:44.860
she do such a thing?

21:45.270 --> 21:47.400
What's worth committing suicide for?

21:48.560 --> 21:49.690
She was too fragile.

21:53.590 --> 21:54.280
Mom.

21:55.240 --> 21:56.730
I bought you a foot basin.

21:57.030 --> 21:58.200
Soak your feet in your free time.

21:58.200 --> 21:59.660
It's good for your health.

21:59.720 --> 22:00.580
I don't want it.

22:00.720 --> 22:02.320
You're wasting money again.

22:04.880 --> 22:05.880
Don't touch them.

22:07.510 --> 22:08.770
These are for your dad.

22:13.990 --> 22:15.310
After you go back to Lihai,

22:15.310 --> 22:16.970
go see Uncle Ding.

22:17.190 --> 22:18.430
He's not doing well.

22:21.200 --> 22:22.240
Why is he back?

22:24.790 --> 22:26.320
They say that he got cancer.

22:27.280 --> 22:28.530
He couldn't be cured abroad.

22:28.530 --> 22:29.860
So he wanted to come back

22:29.890 --> 22:31.220
and return to his roots.

22:33.920 --> 22:36.000
I've been quite busy with school lately.

22:36.000 --> 22:36.920
I might not

22:37.110 --> 22:38.200
have the time.

22:40.110 --> 22:41.520
Why are you so selfish?

22:42.960 --> 22:45.000
You only care about your own business.

22:45.000 --> 22:46.070
Do you know how much

22:46.070 --> 22:47.270
he helped our family?

22:47.920 --> 22:49.920
Our school was shut down and merged.

22:50.000 --> 22:51.030
If Uncle Ding hadn't

22:51.030 --> 22:52.160
stepped in to help,

22:52.160 --> 22:54.420
do you know how much less pension I'd get,

22:54.720 --> 22:58.120
and how much less medical insurance
would cover if I got sick?

23:01.070 --> 23:01.590
Mom,

23:02.510 --> 23:04.240
if you don't have enough money,

23:04.310 --> 23:05.590
you can just tell me.

23:06.030 --> 23:07.380
Is it about money?

23:07.720 --> 23:08.720
In your heart,

23:08.720 --> 23:10.650
this family simply doesn't exist.

23:12.240 --> 23:14.030
Uncle Ding was just

23:14.310 --> 23:15.960
your dad's little underling back then,

23:15.960 --> 23:18.030
but he values relationships
much more than you do.

23:18.030 --> 23:20.400
He sends things every holiday.

23:23.480 --> 23:24.960
The same goes for this time.

23:24.960 --> 23:26.070
I didn't ask him.

23:26.440 --> 23:28.030
He heard about it himself

23:28.030 --> 23:29.160
and offered to help.

23:30.270 --> 23:31.010
But,

23:31.550 --> 23:33.310
you're quite unhappy.

23:33.680 --> 23:34.810
Baffling.

23:37.070 --> 23:38.600
Just go when you are told to.

23:39.160 --> 23:41.490
Don't be as ignorant
as when you were a kid.

24:09.000 --> 24:10.060
Does it sound good?

24:10.160 --> 24:11.110
Yes.

24:12.200 --> 24:13.610
Thank you, Dad.

25:43.670 --> 25:44.300
Master,

25:44.580 --> 25:45.700
you heard it too.

25:45.820 --> 25:47.070
First, the poisoned crabs,

25:47.070 --> 25:48.240
then the rescue team.

25:48.240 --> 25:50.370
How could there be such a coincidence?

25:50.510 --> 25:52.110
Let me investigate further.

25:52.200 --> 25:53.270
Issue me a letter of introduction

25:53.270 --> 25:55.720
and let me verify it
with the Immigration Office.

25:55.720 --> 25:56.640
I'm begging you.

25:56.640 --> 25:58.200
Regarding the telecom fraud,

25:58.200 --> 26:00.480
I have already contacted
our CID colleagues.

26:00.480 --> 26:01.510
It's different.

26:01.590 --> 26:03.790
These people never showed their faces.

26:04.000 --> 26:05.270
They just grabbed a random photo online

26:05.270 --> 26:07.070
and used it as a profile picture.

26:07.680 --> 26:08.750
Xia Yi

26:08.750 --> 26:10.350
is a living person.

26:10.920 --> 26:12.440
That's a great lead.

26:12.550 --> 26:13.160
Isn't it?

26:14.070 --> 26:15.960
Have you finished your own work?

26:15.960 --> 26:16.440
I have.

26:16.880 --> 26:17.540
The report,

26:17.830 --> 26:19.030
the monthly summary,

26:19.030 --> 26:21.560
and the 5,000-word work report
you asked for—

26:22.030 --> 26:22.720
I wrote them all.

26:22.720 --> 26:24.350
Not a single punctuation mark is missing.

26:24.350 --> 26:26.750
What about the correspondent copy
for Lihai Daily?

26:26.750 --> 26:29.150
The correspondent copy for Lihai Daily...

26:46.160 --> 26:46.680
Mr. Li.

26:47.680 --> 26:48.750
Chief Hu wants you
to run an errand for him.

26:48.750 --> 26:49.920
He said there is a foreigner
in our jurisdiction

26:49.920 --> 26:51.070
whose visa has expired or something.

26:51.070 --> 26:51.870
He wants you to go

26:51.870 --> 26:54.200
to the Immigration Office to ask about it.

26:54.350 --> 26:55.950
You can just call...

26:56.350 --> 26:57.750
Just make a phone call...

27:04.510 --> 27:06.240
I've already prepared
the letter of introduction for you.

27:06.240 --> 27:07.790
Don't delay your own work.

27:09.410 --> 27:12.330
[Mingde International Hospital,
Lihai City]

27:14.830 --> 27:17.580
[VVIP suite] [Ding Zhibo]

27:21.750 --> 27:22.880
You must be Yan Ling.

27:30.680 --> 27:32.010
Have a seat. Have a seat.

27:33.830 --> 27:35.190
About my mom's retirement,

27:35.190 --> 27:35.940
thank you.

27:37.310 --> 27:38.750
She's had it tough on her own.

27:38.750 --> 27:40.080
Since you were too busy,

27:40.110 --> 27:42.270
I had to lend a hand. Take a seat.

27:46.590 --> 27:47.440
Over the years,

27:47.440 --> 27:48.160
I've treated

27:48.160 --> 27:50.160
your family's affairs as my own.

27:50.200 --> 27:51.140
You know that.

27:52.750 --> 27:53.420
Thank you.

27:55.070 --> 27:56.800
I'm not looking for a thank you.

27:57.880 --> 27:59.210
It's been so many years,

27:59.550 --> 28:00.680
and I haven't heard from you at all.

28:00.680 --> 28:02.410
You even avoided me on purpose.

28:02.550 --> 28:04.010
It really breaks my heart.

28:08.160 --> 28:09.760
Your mom told me everything.

28:10.160 --> 28:12.160
You've made great progress lately.

28:13.030 --> 28:14.030
That's very good.

28:14.790 --> 28:15.750
If your dad knew,

28:16.230 --> 28:18.360
he would definitely be very relieved.

28:21.200 --> 28:21.720
Indeed.

28:23.930 --> 28:25.230
Back then,

28:26.070 --> 28:27.470
we both had our problems.

28:28.480 --> 28:30.160
We should find a chance to clear the air.

28:30.160 --> 28:31.160
What do you think?

28:32.150 --> 28:32.880
Also...

28:35.440 --> 28:36.440
I'm divorced now.

28:39.750 --> 28:40.830
The dosage, I think...

28:40.830 --> 28:42.480
As long as his mental state is stable,

28:42.480 --> 28:43.340
that's enough.

28:43.550 --> 28:44.270
Okay, Dr. Luo.

28:44.270 --> 28:45.720
We'll talk about it later.

28:45.720 --> 28:47.320
No problem. Call me anytime.

28:47.350 --> 28:47.790
Okay.

28:47.920 --> 28:49.480
Looking forward to working together more.

28:49.480 --> 28:50.050
Alright, see you.

28:50.050 --> 28:51.250
See you, Director He.

28:54.960 --> 28:55.540
Ms. Yan?

28:58.550 --> 28:59.640
What a coincidence.

28:59.640 --> 29:00.270
Dr. Luo.

29:00.520 --> 29:01.880
I thought it was you from the back.

29:01.880 --> 29:03.550
Didn't you go back to your hometown?

29:03.550 --> 29:03.920
Yes,

29:05.590 --> 29:07.190
I just got back this morning.

29:08.310 --> 29:09.140
I knew it.

29:09.400 --> 29:10.160
Now that you're back,

29:10.160 --> 29:12.420
you wouldn't just not tell me on purpose.

29:15.480 --> 29:17.210
What happened to your clothes?

29:19.790 --> 29:21.390
I accidentally got it dirty.

29:21.590 --> 29:22.830
I don't think it'll wash out,

29:22.830 --> 29:23.880
so I threw it away.

29:26.590 --> 29:28.720
I came here to help with a consultation.

29:28.720 --> 29:29.960
There's a critically ill patient here

29:29.960 --> 29:31.880
who developed delirium after surgery.

29:31.880 --> 29:33.010
He was not very lucid

29:33.110 --> 29:34.710
and almost pulled out his IV.

29:35.680 --> 29:36.540
What about you?

29:36.750 --> 29:38.280
Are you here to see a doctor?

29:39.920 --> 29:40.640
I came to

29:41.200 --> 29:42.200
visit a relative.

29:44.920 --> 29:45.480
Then...

29:46.270 --> 29:46.930
tonight...

29:49.830 --> 29:50.680
Oh, right.

29:51.550 --> 29:52.430
We agreed

29:52.590 --> 29:54.850
to have a meal together after I came back.

29:54.920 --> 29:56.780
I'm not forcing you to eat with me.

29:56.830 --> 29:57.430
No, no, no.

29:57.510 --> 29:58.590
It was my fault.

29:59.350 --> 30:00.440
I promised you

30:00.480 --> 30:02.080
-that I'll come back—
-Yeah.

30:03.510 --> 30:04.400
You promised

30:04.480 --> 30:06.280
to call me as soon as you got back.

30:08.840 --> 30:10.840
But actually, I'm not free tonight.

30:11.110 --> 30:11.710
Next time.

30:12.960 --> 30:13.690
You go first.

30:13.890 --> 30:15.480
I still have something to do here.

30:15.480 --> 30:16.460
Okay.

30:17.960 --> 30:19.760
When we both have time next time,

30:19.790 --> 30:20.720
I'll ask you out.

30:20.920 --> 30:21.480
Okay.

30:22.680 --> 30:23.400
I'll go then.

30:23.400 --> 30:23.930
Bye-bye.

30:36.820 --> 30:37.720
[Pediatric Clinic] [Pulmonology]

30:42.510 --> 30:43.160
Hello.

30:44.440 --> 30:46.370
Are there inpatient wards inside?

30:52.170 --> 30:56.420
[VVIP suite] [Ding Zhibo]

31:00.210 --> 31:03.290
[Ding Zhibo]

31:06.130 --> 31:08.710
[Ding Zhibo,
Oceanvision International Group]

31:09.040 --> 31:11.650
[Oceanvision International Group Co., Ltd.]

31:15.960 --> 31:19.140
[Yan Ling]

31:19.450 --> 31:21.590
[Yan Ling, School of Atmospheric and Oceanic Sciences –
Model Teacher of Ethics]

31:21.900 --> 31:23.400
[Yan Ling – Academic Profile]

31:25.820 --> 31:27.940
[Yan Ling earned her bachelor's
from Lihai University in 2005.]

31:26.070 --> 31:28.350
You did your grad studies
at Lihai University?

31:28.350 --> 31:31.080
You took an extra year
to complete your master's.

31:33.890 --> 31:35.870
[Lihai University]

31:35.890 --> 31:39.720
[Lihai University]
[Yan Ling, Lihai University, 2005 - 2009]

31:42.030 --> 31:49.060
[Mistress Beaten—
Top Student Exposed as a Tycoon's Kept Woman]

31:52.240 --> 31:53.160
There was quite a scene

31:53.160 --> 31:54.770
outside the library today.

31:57.440 --> 31:59.000
She ended up as someone's mistress,

31:59.000 --> 32:01.330
and even got beaten by the guy's daughter.

32:14.890 --> 32:18.110
[Oceanvision International Group]

32:22.780 --> 32:27.130
[The time will come to ride the wind and break the waves,
to set my sails across the sea.]

32:29.370 --> 32:32.690
[Group style]

32:31.270 --> 32:33.270
The founder
of Oceanvision International Group

32:32.690 --> 32:33.640
[Development History]

32:33.830 --> 32:36.430
served on ocean-going vessels
for many years,

32:36.750 --> 32:38.520
starting as a cadet,

32:37.690 --> 32:47.650
[Oceanvision International Group]

32:39.030 --> 32:41.940
then Third Officer, Second Officer,
Chief Officer,

32:41.940 --> 32:43.400
until he became a captain.

32:44.000 --> 32:45.330
Looking back on it,

32:45.480 --> 32:47.680
Ding Zhibo is always filled with pride.

32:47.880 --> 32:49.060
This experience

32:49.550 --> 32:50.580
gave me

32:51.200 --> 32:52.730
a heart as vast as the ocean,

32:53.240 --> 32:54.310
a will of steel,

32:54.710 --> 32:56.510
and indomitable courage,

32:56.750 --> 32:59.580
so that in my future ventures,

32:58.770 --> 33:04.180
[Oceanvision International Group]

32:59.640 --> 33:00.660
I can

33:01.030 --> 33:02.470
keep pushing forward

33:03.030 --> 33:04.360
through wind and waves.

33:08.240 --> 33:09.420
The fate of an enterprise

33:09.270 --> 33:13.790
[Oceanvision International Group]

33:09.790 --> 33:10.870
is like a ship

33:11.240 --> 33:13.440
sailing across a boundless ocean.

33:14.200 --> 33:15.510
Calm on the surface,

33:15.960 --> 33:16.830
but beneath it,

33:17.000 --> 33:18.800
powerful undercurrents surge.

33:18.990 --> 33:22.190
[Oceanvision International Group]

33:19.110 --> 33:20.150
A person's life

33:20.880 --> 33:21.790
is the same.

33:23.270 --> 33:25.270
Ding Zhibo's only son,
who just started college,

33:25.270 --> 33:26.970
died in a car accident abroad.

33:27.270 --> 33:28.180
When the news hit,

33:28.180 --> 33:30.160
Ding Zhibo and his wife were devastated.

33:30.160 --> 33:31.400
But he told his wife,

33:31.420 --> 33:31.970
"We...

33:35.220 --> 33:37.500
[Oceanvision International Group]

33:38.440 --> 33:40.350
Ding Zhibo's only son,
who just started college,

33:40.150 --> 33:44.850
[Oceanvision International Group]

33:40.350 --> 33:42.170
died in a car accident abroad.

33:42.350 --> 33:43.350
When the news hit,

33:43.440 --> 33:45.480
Ding Zhibo and his wife were devastated.

33:45.480 --> 33:46.680
But he told his wife,

33:46.750 --> 33:48.000
we lost our son,

33:48.350 --> 33:50.110
but Oceanvision International
is our other child,

33:49.650 --> 33:50.560
[There was quite a scene
outside the library today.]

33:50.200 --> 33:51.510
the only child."

33:50.590 --> 33:51.340
[No way. The so-called untouchable
top student from the Oceanography School]

33:51.370 --> 33:52.040
[ended up being someone's mistress,]

33:52.060 --> 33:52.560
[and even got confronted
and beaten by the guy's daughter.]

33:52.590 --> 33:53.120
[That cup of coffee she threw—
what a scene.]

33:52.790 --> 33:55.320
So the person who hit you
wasn't his daughter.

33:56.240 --> 33:57.310
Who could it be?

34:09.949 --> 34:12.060
You clearly can write well.

34:12.400 --> 34:13.440
If you'd put in this effort earlier,

34:13.440 --> 34:14.920
you wouldn't have been scolded so much.

34:14.920 --> 34:16.360
Yes, that's all thanks

34:16.590 --> 34:17.590
to your guidance.

34:17.880 --> 34:19.360
It's helped me a lot.

34:24.280 --> 34:26.590
Request for assistance with investigation?

34:26.590 --> 34:27.670
What are you doing?

34:29.190 --> 34:29.760
Master,

34:31.150 --> 34:32.330
although

34:32.590 --> 34:34.630
the Immigration Office helped us verify

34:34.630 --> 34:36.489
the authenticity of Xia Yi's—no,

34:36.510 --> 34:38.880
Pongsri Leekpa's passport,

34:39.280 --> 34:39.920
but

34:40.030 --> 34:41.000
I called

34:41.000 --> 34:43.659
the contact number
he filled in when he entered.

34:44.190 --> 34:45.440
It's a tour guide's namber
from a travel agency.

34:45.440 --> 34:47.150
And he has absolutely
no impression of him.

34:47.150 --> 34:47.840
Moreover,

34:47.840 --> 34:49.230
since he entered the country,

34:49.230 --> 34:51.440
he left no registration records

34:51.440 --> 34:52.400
at any local police station.

34:52.400 --> 34:53.190
He hasn't checked into any hotels,

34:53.190 --> 34:54.280
taken flights,

34:54.280 --> 34:55.150
high-speed rail,

34:55.150 --> 34:56.170
or trains.

34:57.880 --> 34:59.900
That's way too unusual.

35:01.400 --> 35:03.780
So, after thinking about it,

35:04.800 --> 35:06.530
there is only one possibility.

35:07.230 --> 35:09.360
He must have another identity in China

35:09.880 --> 35:11.920
So you want to find this person

35:11.920 --> 35:14.120
in the household registration system?

35:15.550 --> 35:17.000
This doesn't just need my approval.

35:17.000 --> 35:18.880
It also has to be reported
to the Municipal Bureau.

35:18.880 --> 35:21.540
-I know. But we have—
-Why should I approve this?

35:22.670 --> 35:24.190
We can completely sync this clue

35:24.190 --> 35:25.670
to our colleagues in CID

35:25.920 --> 35:27.240
and let them follow up.

35:27.550 --> 35:29.190
You're just refusing to let this go.

35:29.190 --> 35:32.110
You feel you were deceived
and played by him,

35:32.470 --> 35:33.670
and lost face, right?

35:57.670 --> 35:58.760
I... I can't say

35:58.760 --> 36:00.000
I've never thought about it that way,

36:00.000 --> 36:00.480
Master.

36:01.000 --> 36:01.960
But now,

36:01.960 --> 36:04.360
this is no longer about pride.

36:05.190 --> 36:05.650
Master,

36:06.360 --> 36:08.070
the victim Missile
and the others encountered,

36:08.070 --> 36:09.360
the one who jumped off the building,

36:09.360 --> 36:10.400
was saved by them.

36:12.550 --> 36:14.080
But what about Jian Leilei?

36:16.880 --> 36:19.760
I saw Jian Leilei's parents
crying in utter despair

36:26.000 --> 36:26.760
in front of me

36:29.030 --> 36:31.360
that day.

36:32.670 --> 36:34.440
I thought if I should have tried
a little harder,

36:34.440 --> 36:36.390
held on a little longer,

36:36.550 --> 36:38.550
could I have saved them all?

36:38.550 --> 36:41.080
I obviously had contact
with Pongsri Leekpa.

36:41.920 --> 36:43.110
I'm this close to him.

36:43.110 --> 36:45.360
And I feel like I could reach his true face.

36:45.360 --> 36:46.800
If I just give up now,

36:46.800 --> 36:47.450
what if

36:47.510 --> 36:49.470
the colleagues in CID get careless

36:49.800 --> 36:50.800
and don't notice him?

36:50.800 --> 36:52.860
Wouldn't that bastard just get away?

36:56.230 --> 36:56.590
I...

36:56.800 --> 36:57.710
I don't know how to say it.

36:57.710 --> 36:58.370
I have to...

36:58.710 --> 37:00.760
I have to live up to this badge.

37:00.760 --> 37:01.230
Master,

37:01.230 --> 37:03.840
otherwise, I won't be able
to sleep at night.

37:03.960 --> 37:04.550
Really, Master.

37:04.550 --> 37:06.360
These past few days,
when I close my eyes at night,

37:06.360 --> 37:07.800
all I see are poisoned crabs,

37:07.800 --> 37:08.870
rescue teams,

37:08.890 --> 37:10.150
Pongsri Leekpa,

37:10.150 --> 37:10.960
and Xia Yi.

37:10.960 --> 37:12.550
I... I'm almost driven crazy.

37:12.550 --> 37:13.480
I've already been...

37:13.480 --> 37:14.880
almost driven mad by him.

37:17.840 --> 37:18.970
Don't embarrass me.

37:20.060 --> 37:24.630
[Dongchuan Public Security Bureau]

37:24.910 --> 37:29.130
[2. 18 Task Force]

37:26.000 --> 37:27.120
Look at this case.

37:27.140 --> 37:28.030
It fits the pattern

37:28.030 --> 37:29.890
of this new type of telecom fraud.

37:30.070 --> 37:31.360
-I think we can—
-Captain Wang,

37:31.360 --> 37:31.960
he's here.

37:32.320 --> 37:32.650
Okay.

37:33.840 --> 37:34.970
I'll leave it to you.

37:35.190 --> 37:35.950
Carry on.

37:52.480 --> 37:53.240
Cai Zhiyu.

37:55.070 --> 37:56.270
They call you Caicai,

37:56.760 --> 37:57.280
right?

38:00.710 --> 38:02.840
Tell us about this ISYC coin you set up.

38:03.840 --> 38:04.770
How does it work?

38:08.080 --> 38:10.820
[Shared Coin]

38:08.510 --> 38:10.920
The exchange rate trends on your website

38:11.480 --> 38:12.840
are entirely fabricated,

38:12.840 --> 38:13.360
right?

38:14.630 --> 38:16.170
Whether it goes up or down,

38:16.440 --> 38:17.700
you have the final say.

38:19.440 --> 38:21.110
I heard you used to be a network engineer

38:21.110 --> 38:22.510
at a major tech company.

38:23.440 --> 38:24.970
Making such a small website

38:25.150 --> 38:27.080
is a waste of your talent, isn't it?

38:27.840 --> 38:30.040
I don't understand what you're saying.

38:30.670 --> 38:31.870
You are very smart.

38:33.230 --> 38:34.510
One crew chats with clients

38:34.510 --> 38:37.360
and plays the emotional angle
to hook them,

38:37.840 --> 38:39.880
another rigs the charts on the site,

38:40.800 --> 38:43.400
and a third group handles
the money transfers.

38:45.190 --> 38:47.920
The clients' funds
don't go through the website,

38:48.070 --> 38:51.120
but directly into another bank account.

38:51.280 --> 38:53.360
As the middle link,

38:53.360 --> 38:56.390
you neither touch the funds
nor the clients.

38:56.480 --> 38:58.100
It seems to be the safest.

38:59.480 --> 39:01.210
But have you ever thought about

39:01.360 --> 39:04.110
why you were the first one we caught?

39:07.150 --> 39:09.350
You thought using multi-layer proxies

39:10.190 --> 39:11.880
to mask your IP address—

39:11.880 --> 39:13.880
and even routing through overseas servers

39:13.880 --> 39:15.550
to cover your tracks—

39:15.550 --> 39:16.680
would keep you safe?

39:17.150 --> 39:20.150
Then, where did the domain name
of ISYC coin come from?

39:21.670 --> 39:22.760
If I were you,

39:23.670 --> 39:25.110
I wouldn't be stupid enough

39:25.110 --> 39:27.280
to register a domain name
with my own email.

39:27.280 --> 39:29.880
I didn't. I didn't use my own email to...

39:34.840 --> 39:36.900
You indeed didn't use your own email.

39:37.400 --> 39:39.930
You had someone
buy an overseas email online.

39:41.550 --> 39:43.600
But every move leaves a trace.

39:43.840 --> 39:46.150
We found the buyer
through the domain name,

39:46.150 --> 39:47.630
and naturally found you.

39:50.550 --> 39:52.530
You were too careless.

39:52.960 --> 39:55.280
You only cared
about the safety of your accomplices,

39:55.280 --> 39:57.030
but no one cared about yours.

39:59.640 --> 40:01.080
[Name: Pongsri Leekpa]

40:01.280 --> 40:02.140
Do you know him?

40:04.710 --> 40:05.230
No.

40:05.580 --> 40:07.160
[Name: Pongsri Leekpa]

40:10.050 --> 40:11.830
[Name: Pongsri Leekpa]

40:10.480 --> 40:11.540
How about this one?

40:17.230 --> 40:18.510
You must know this one.

40:19.070 --> 40:21.000
You two even took a photo together.

40:25.660 --> 40:27.840
Don't think you are an unbreakable alliance!

40:27.840 --> 40:29.590
We've been watching you for a long time,

40:29.590 --> 40:31.790
and this isn't the first or second case.

40:32.190 --> 40:34.120
You can deny knowing anyone today.

40:34.840 --> 40:35.880
Get a good sleep.

40:36.510 --> 40:38.110
Think it through carefully.

40:38.400 --> 40:40.190
How did he bring clients to you?

40:41.030 --> 40:42.670
Think about your previous link

40:42.670 --> 40:44.270
and who the next link is.

40:45.230 --> 40:46.710
The more you remember,

40:47.440 --> 40:49.400
the more trouble they'll be in,

40:50.110 --> 40:52.190
and the less trouble you'll have.

40:52.880 --> 40:53.610
Understand?

40:57.710 --> 40:58.360
Follow me.

41:10.150 --> 41:12.440
Did you find out where Pongsri went
after entering the country?

41:12.440 --> 41:13.320
Not yet.

41:13.400 --> 41:14.110
But

41:15.190 --> 41:17.190
the Immigration Office said

41:17.190 --> 41:18.440
there's an Officer Li

41:18.440 --> 41:20.700
who is also looking into Pongsri Leekpa.

41:23.480 --> 41:25.340
Find Officer Li's profile for me.

41:25.710 --> 41:27.040
Okay, I'll go right now.

41:29.930 --> 41:34.440
[The Dark Romance]

41:42.150 --> 41:44.060
Why isn't your dad back yet?

41:44.150 --> 41:45.940
The food is getting cold.

41:47.070 --> 41:48.670
How about I page him?

41:49.360 --> 41:51.160
How can he check it while riding?

41:52.280 --> 41:53.500
You eat. You eat.

41:59.690 --> 42:00.620
I want some, too.

42:03.760 --> 42:05.370
You little foodie.

42:07.360 --> 42:08.510
All you know is eating.

42:08.510 --> 42:09.170
It's my dad.

42:09.530 --> 42:10.590
It must be your dad.

42:12.150 --> 42:13.370
Hello, where are you?

42:13.630 --> 42:15.550
I... I am. Who's this?
